Service Intelligence Einstein Conversation Mining Dashboard

Review key reasons why your customers reach out for help with Einstein AI. See top topics or contact reasons by volume, duration of conversations, times conversations pass from a bot to an agent, average cost per interaction, and more.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions

In Einstein Conversation Mining, you can see the details for the report (1). Open Einstein Conversation Mining from the dashboard (2), and view the high-level details about Einstein Conversation Mining (3). See top topics and contact reasons by volume (4). See topics by average duration, turns, and volume (5).

CONVERSATION MINING KPI
Report name.
ECM Report/analysis creation date.
Date range of ECM analysis.
Selected language for analysis.
Percent of topics found in given analysis.
Total conversations associated with each contact reason.
Number of contacts for a given ECM analysis or topic.
Percentage of total contacts by contact type.
Duration of conversations associated with this topic.
Average number of turns (conversation responses) in a given conversation.
Estimated cost based on hourly rate and average handle time.
